<BaseLayout title="Chant Cards" description="Public chant cards from Vaelinya.">
  <section class="page-section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Artefacts</p>
    <h1>Chant cards</h1>
    <p class="lede">Chant cards are small repeatable pieces that hold rhythm, memory, learning, and shared voice.</p>
    <p>They help words stay alive through repetition, fairness, counting, learning, and communal remembering. A small card can carry more than instruction.</p>
    <p>A chant card gives a phrase enough shape to be spoken, remembered, and passed from one person to another.</p>
    <div class="link-list">
      <a href="/language/lexicon/">Language and sound</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
